@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cgvzmr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin(v2) + ((v1 + 0.06 * v1 + 0.09) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.88)))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.45) + (v1 + 0.65 * tmp + 0.89)) / 0.21)
    v2 = 0.49
    v0 = (0.01 * ((v1 + 0.19 - tmp + 0.29) - 0.68))
    tmp = wp.exp((v1 / (tmp + 0.24 / v2 + 0.89)))
    data[tid] = v0
